data.description: Welcome to this cozy abode nestled in the heart of a serene suburban community, offering the perfect blend of comfort and potential. This quaint 2 bedroom home (with the potential for a 3rd bedroom) 1 bathroom home sits on almost a fenced in quarter acre of land. Many of the major updates have been completed in the last few years, including: Furnace, Central Air, Electrical Service Panel and Plumbing.  This home is perfect for a first time home owner looking to experience the joys of home ownership, or the investor looking for the ideal rental property.  This is a prime location in Pontiac just one block from Terry Lake and close proximity to Hawthorne park and Woodward Ave.  It will be hard to find better value in a home...and the location speaks for itself! Don't miss the chance to explore the potential and possibilities this property holds. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and start envisioning your future in this charming suburban haven! BATVAI  NOTE: The wheel chair ramp will be removed within 30 days of closing unless buyer would like to work out something with PACE to have it remain at the home.
